build flow:

1. setting your tool chain:
export PATH=~/Your_Toolchain_PATH/:$PATH
for example export PATH=~/prebuilts/gcc/linux-x86/x86/x86_64-linux-android-4.8/bin:$PATH

2. build command:
kernel
======
1. cd linux/kernel/
2. cp arch/x86/configs/x86_64_byt_defconfig .config
3. make menufconfig
4. $make -j32 

======

Contact Lenovo support for information on obtaining Open Source code.
